<h2>Prospective Students</h2>
<p>If you are interested in any of the following research areas for your graduate studies at NUAA, you are welcome to contact me by email. Please provide a brief introduction about yourself and attach your most recent CV. </p>
<ul>
<li><p>Remote condition monitoring in digitalized offshore wind farms</p>
</li>
<li><p>Cooperative control of wind turbines in large wind farms</p>
</li>
<li><p>Fault-tolerant and cyber-resilient control of hybrid microgrids</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Qualified and eligible candidates can be considered for stipends, and supported to apply for CSC, NMGS, and NUAA Postgraduate Scholarships available to international students. </p>
<p>For more information about NUAA (rankings, programs, scholarships, application requirements, etc.) visit this <a href="http://ciee.nuaa.edu.cn/home" target="_blank"><b>[link]</b></a></p>
